method 2: conda install
https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/46579831

Install(Already installed the Anaconda3):
1. check the python version: 
    import sys
    print(sys.version)
2. create the tensorflow environment
    conda create -n tensorflow python=3.7.3
3. active tensorflow
    conda activate tensorflow
4. pip uninstall tensorflow
5. conda install tensorflow

Setup
1. update Anaconda
   launch Anaconda Navigator
2. applications -> tensorflow
3. Install Spyder(tensorflow)

Test
import tensorflow as tf
print(tf.__version__)
